==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Congealment
<hw>Con*geal"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The
act or the process of congealing; congeliation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which is formed by congelation; a clot.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Wash the <qex>congealment</qex> from your wounds.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Congee</ent>⟦br⟧
